OL,3,CIran running low on drones and
OL,4,Cmissiles, western officials believe
OL,6,FIran can only keep up the current rate
OL,7,Fof attacks across the Middle East for
OL,8,Fseveral more days, western officials
OL,9,Fbelieve, and the pace of their attacks
OL,10,Fhas already slowed.
OL,12,FThe intelligence picture suggests this
OL,13,Fis probably due to the rate of US and
OL,14,FIsraeli attacks on launch sites and
OL,15,Fstorage depots within Iran.
OL,17,FBut they can't rule out the Iranians
OL,18,Fslowing the pace of their attacks to
OL,19,Fextend the war and say this could
OL,20,Fstill go on 'for some time'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
