OL,3,CIran running low on drones and
OL,4,Cmissiles, western officials believe
OL,6,FSo far, ten different countries have
OL,7,Fbeen targeted with hundreds of
OL,8,Fballistic missiles and hundreds of
OL,9,Fdrones.
OL,11,FOfficials say those countries have
OL,12,Ffired through a considerable quantity
OL,13,Fof their Patriot and other air defence
OL,14,Fmissile stockpiles.
OL,16,FBritish experts who have worked
OL,17,Falongside the Ukrainians to counter
OL,18,Fdrone attacks there are preparing to
OL,19,Ffly to the Middle East to advise some
OL,20,Fof those nations on how best to
OL,21,Frespond to the threat of drones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
