OL,3,CIran running low on drones and
OL,4,Cmissiles, western officials believe
OL,6,FOfficials have also revealed that they
OL,7,Fdo not believe the Shahed type drone
OL,8,Fwhich struck RAF Akrotiri in Cyprus to
OL,9,Fhave been fired from Iran. This is
OL,10,Fbased on the range and capabilities of
OL,11,Fthat particular drone.
OL,13,FThe officials won't comment on where
OL,14,Fthey think the drone came from, but
OL,15,FLebanon, which is much closer to
OL,16,FCyprus and is home to Iranian proxies
OL,17,Fsuch as Hezbollah, would seem to be a
OL,18,Fpossible launch site.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
