OL,3,CIran running low on drones and
OL,4,Cmissiles, western officials believe
OL,6,FThe UK warship HMS Dragon is currently
OL,7,Fbeing readied to sail to Cyprus, but
OL,8,Fis unlikely to leave until next week.
OL,10,FThe Type 45 destroyer had been
OL,11,Fundergoing routine maintenance and is
OL,12,Fnow being re-armed before sailing for
OL,13,Fthe eastern Mediterranean. The two
OL,14,FWildcat helicopters which can fly from
OL,15,FDragon are likely to head out there
OL,16,Fsooner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
