OL,6,FSo far the British bases on Diego
OL,7,FGarcia and at RAF Fairford in
OL,8,FGloucestershire have not hosted any of
OL,9,Fthe US aircraft which the Prime
OL,10,FMinister says can use them to target
OL,11,FIranian launch sites, but officials
OL,12,Fexpect those aircraft to start
OL,13,Farriving in the coming days.
